name: CCP Merch Confirmation Code
description:
After you purchase a merch NFT from us on H=N, you will need the confirmation code from *this* NFT to redeem your merch.


This NFT is an Interactive OBJKT that generates and displays a unique confirmation code based on your own wallet address. You must have your wallet synced to the hic et nunc website (i.e. logged in / connected) to generate a confirmation code. 

Once you've collected the confirmation code from this page, send an email to redeem@cryptocampfirepodcast.com that includes the code, your wallet address, and your shipping address to redeem!

Did we mention this NFT can be collected all by itself? Just in case you want to collect one ;)
